description:
Minecraft Tutorials Playlist ► http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLEB388783144C45A8
This minecraft tutorial video will showcase all the cool things you can do with flags in minecraft 1.8. These were added in shapshot 14w30a and this video will show you everything you need to know about them!

Minecraft 1.8: Snapshot 14w30a Banners, Flags, Skulls & FPS Boost!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TsmNILp3RHw&list=PL7VmhWGNRxKixIX8tWEQn-BnYKE9AaAXk

Minecraft: Mass Breeding Machine Tutorial
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jUJ7oDOhXTA&list=PLEB388783144C45A8

Minecraft: Automatic Cooked Chicken Farm Tutorial
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tWT_WCTFUvA&list=PLEB388783144C45A8
